%s will cause all custom html tags to be stripped out.'=>'没有 %s 的用户进行修订将导致所有自定义 HTML 标签被删除。','Revision by a user who does not have the unfiltered_html capability will cause all custom html tags to be stripped out.'=>'没有 unfiltered_html 能力的用户进行的修订将导致所有自定义 HTML 标签被删除。','Broadest compat including Elementor, Divi, Beaver Builder'=>'兼容性最广，包括 Elementor、Divi、Beaver Builder','Standard storage schema for broadest 3rd party compat'=>'标准存储架构以实现最广泛的第三方兼容性','Enhanced Revision access control with PublishPress plugins'=>'通过 PublishPress 插件增强修订访问控制','In enhanced mode, a Revision\'s status is stored by standard WordPress schema. Some plugins are incompatible.'=>'在增强模式下，修订的状态由标准 WordPress 架构存储。一些插件不兼容。','Prevent Revision creation if the post already has another Revision in progress.'=>'如果帖子已经有其他修订正在进行，则防止创建修订。','Work around cache plugin conflicts by requerying for revisions before suppressing the New Revision link.'=>'通过在抑制新修订链接之前重新查询修订，解决缓存插件冲突。','If the user does not have a regular Edit link, recaption the %s link as "Edit."'=>'如果用户没有常规编辑链接，将 %s 链接重新命名为 "编辑"。','Default labels are "Not Submitted for Approval", "Submitted for Approval", "Scheduled Revision"'=>'默认标签为 "未提交审批"、"已提交审批"、"计划修订"','Enable published content to be copied, edited, submitted for approval and managed on the %sNew Revisions%s screen.'=>'启用已发布的内容在 %s新修订%s 屏幕上被复制、编辑、提交审批和管理。','Submit Revision capabilities'=>'提交修订能力','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require Submit Revision capabilities (revise_posts, revise_others_pages, etc.)'=>'如果用户无法编辑已发布的帖子，则需要提交修订能力（revise_posts、revise_others_pages等）','When a %s is published, update post publish date to current time.'=>'当 %s 发布时，将帖子发布日期更新为当前时间。','When a %s is published, update post modified date to current time.'=>'当 %s 发布时，将帖子修改日期更新为当前时间。','When a new revision is created by any user who is allowed to submit revisions, automatically submit it.'=>'当任何被允许提交修订的用户创建新修订时，自动提交它。','Auto-submit revisions if the user can directly edit the main post.'=>'如果用户可以直接编辑主帖子，则自动提交修订。','This allows immediate approval within the Compare screen. If disabled, a Preview link is provided instead.'=>'这允许在比较屏幕中立即批准。如果禁用，则提供预览链接。','If a currently published post or page is edited and a future date set, the change will not be applied until the selected date.'=>'如果编辑当前已发布的帖子或页面并设置未来日期，则更改将在所选日期之前不生效。','Publish scheduled revisions using the WP-Cron mechanism. On some sites, publication will fail if this setting is disabled.'=>'使用 WP-Cron 机制发布计划的修订。在某些网站上，如果禁用此设置，则发布将失败。','Publish scheduled revisions asynchronously, via a secondary http request from the server.  This is usually best since it eliminates delay, but some servers may not support it.'=>'通过服务器的二次 http 请求异步发布计划的修订。这通常是最佳选择，因为它消除了延迟，但某些服务器可能不支持。','The WP-Cron trigger is disabled, but scheduled tasks are still excecuted using a custom trigger.'=>'WP-Cron 触发器已禁用，但计划任务仍使用自定义触发器执行。','Caption the button as either "Approve and Publish" or "Approve and Schedule."'=>'将按钮标记为“批准并发布”或“批准并安排”。','This may improve compatibility with some plugins.'=>'这可能提高与某些插件的兼容性。','Control New Revisions access with the %s.'=>'通过 %s 控制新修订的访问。','Control New Revisions access with the manage_revision_queue capability.'=>'通过 manage_revision_queue 能力控制新修订的访问。','Users will need the %s to edit others\' Unsubmitted Revisions.'=>'用户需要 %s 才能编辑其他人的未提交修订。','Users will need the manage_unsubmitted_revisions capability to edit others\' Unsubmitted Revisions.'=>'用户需要 manage_unsubmitted_revisions 能力才能编辑其他人的未提交修订。','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require the %s.'=>'如果用户无法编辑已发布的帖子，则需要 %s。','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require the edit_others_revisions capability.'=>'如果用户无法编辑已发布的帖子，则需要 edit_others_revisions 能力。','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require the list_others_revisions capability.'=>'如果用户无法编辑已发布的帖子，则需要 list_others_revisions 能力。','Bypass the above restrictions for others\' revisions to logged in user\'s own posts.'=>'绕过上述限制，以便其他人的修订可以登录用户自己的帖子。','Regenerate "post has revision" flags'=>'重新生成“帖子有修订”标志',