n its translations.'=>'对于任何翻译已更新（可能通过修订批准）且更新日期晚于其翻译的帖子，设置 "需要更新"。','Show descriptive captions for PublishPress Revisions settings.'=>'显示 PublishPress 修订设置的描述性标题。','Plugin settings, New Revisions contents and related data will be deleted, but only after the last copy of Revisions / Revisions Pro is deleted.'=>'插件设置、新修订内容和相关数据将被删除，但仅在最后一份修订 / 修订专业版被删除后。','Unlock Pro Integrations'=>'解锁专业集成','Upgrade to the Pro version for optimal compatibility and prompt, professional support.'=>'升级到专业版以获得最佳兼容性和及时的专业支持。','Admin'=>'admin','Builder'=>'构建器','Cache'=>'缓存','E-Commerce'=>'电子商务','Fields'=>'字段','Multilingual'=>'多语言','SEO'=>'SEO','Workflow'=>'工作流','Specify which PublishPress Revisions Settings to control network-wide. Unselected settings are controlled separately on each site.'=>'指定要在网络范围内控制哪些 PublishPress 修订设置。未选中的设置将在每个站点上单独控制。','network-wide control of "%s"'=>'在网络范围内控制 "%s"','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','Revert to Defaults'=>'恢复默认设置','All settings in this form (including those on unselected tabs) will be reset to DEFAULTS.  Are you sure?'=>'此表单中的所有设置（包括未选择的选项卡上的设置）将重置为默认值。您确定吗？','Commerce'=>'Commerce','Multilang'=>'Multilang','Community'=>'Community','Pro'=>'Pro','Supported'=>'Supported','Active Plugin'=>'Active Plugin','Supported by PublishPress Revisions'=>'Supported by PublishPress Revisions','Supported by Revisions Pro'=>'Supported by Revisions Pro','Integration Active'=>'集成已激活','Upgrade to Pro to enable this integration'=>'升级到 Pro 以启用此集成','Unlock %s integration to enhance your revisions solution.'=>'解锁 %s 集成以增强您的修订解决方案。','Active Plugin Integration'=>'活动插件集成','Supported Plugin Integration'=>'支持的插件集成','Supported Plugin'=>'支持的插件','Now'=>'现在','Author'=>'作者','(on approval)'=>'(待批准)','Save changes to continue.'=>'保存更改以继续。','Please save changes to the revision before submitting it.'=>'请在提交之前保存对修订的更改。','Preview this Revision'=>'预览此修订','View / Publish'=>'查看 / 发布','View / Approve'=>'查看 / 通过','View / Moderate saved revision'=>'查看 / 审核已保存的修订','View / Submit saved revision'=>'查看 / 提交已保存的